    <header>
      <h1><a href="/uncommon">Uncommon Sense</a></h1>
      <p class="postdate">Length: <strong>47 minutes.</strong> Date recorded: 2011-08</p>
    </header>
    <p><strong>All of my business advice for entrepreneurs. A quick summary of almost everything I've learned. One of my most popular talks.</strong></p>

<p>
This is the talk that a few different conferences paid the big bucks to have me do in-person. But I don't like repeating myself, so I hit record in the studio to share it for free.<br>
<br>
It's split into 8 parts, one subject each:<br>
<br>
1- My background<br>
2- Why are you doing this?<br>
3- Nobody knows the future.<br>
4- Revolution<br>
5- Hit or switch<br>
6- Version 0.1<br>
7- Ideas × Execution<br>
8- CD Baby
</p>
